N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 701.10 - Conflicting rules deemed to conform

State Regulations

Any part of these regulations which is in conflict with rules
and regulations properly adopted by the Committee on Open Government, or its
successor, shall be deemed to be amended to conform to such rules and
regulations, to the extent required by law. Notes
